gs to consider:\n- The `percent` attribute for the `\u003cprogress /\u003e` element is not used by the screen reader. The screen reader is reading from the `valuetext` attribute (viewable in the Browser Toolbox's Accessibility panel when inspecting the element).\n- The displayed value for the remaining bandwidth is rounded unless the value is at the 75% bandwidth threshold (when the value is rounded to the nearest tenth).\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D288991\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290195\n", "files": ["browser/components/ipprotection/content/bandwidth-usage.mjs", "browser/components/ipprotection/tests/browser/browser_ipprotection_bandwidth_precision.js"], "git_node": "786044894c1d8d18767403ee51660dc084754ee3", "git_parents": ["781c8b0151d0a81cc76cc858046f97c5265b74c5"], "node": "97a37a7aa724f02c8e752a7d7c3dae349ef09437", "parents": ["08538e5f6106721773485891648c21b0006ef217"], "tags": []}], "date": 1774547079, "git_changesets": ["786044894c1d8d18767403ee51660dc084754ee3"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25210": {"changesets": [{"author": "Nathan Barrett \u003cnbarrett@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2025172 - Add selfLoading pref to firefox.js  a=diannaS\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D289589\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290144\n", "files": ["browser/app/profile/firefox.js"], "git_node": "a5222584d94e598b544df8b49908d7c4ced97a9a", "git_parents": ["786044894c1d8d18767403ee51660dc084754ee3"], "node": "97b5bb338c5d9a1b05728f70a1519b94ac1807d2", "parents": ["97a37a7aa724f02c8e752a7d7c3dae349ef09437"], "tags": []}], "date": 1774549202, "git_changesets": ["a5222584d94e598b544df8b49908d7c4ced97a9a"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25211": {"changesets": [{"author": "Alastor Wu \u003calastor0325@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2025481 - Add missing shutdown guards to WMFCDMProxy.  a=