u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2023925 - Modernize the SVG filter attribute enums.  a=diannaS\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D289739\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290919\n", "files": ["dom/svg/SVGFEBlendElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFEColorMatrixElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFEComponentTransferElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFECompositeElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFEConvolveMatrixElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFEDisplacementMapElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFEMorphologyElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFETurbulenceElement.cpp", "dom/svg/SVGFilters.cpp", "gfx/ipc/GfxMessageUtils.h", "gfx/src/FilterSupport.cpp", "gfx/src/FilterSupport.h", "layout/svg/CSSFilterInstance.cpp", "layout/svg/FilterInstance.cpp"], "git_node": "8cefe049c93f56ae7588a89f65eb67cf118457f7", "git_parents": ["bede9ea2ab3e7d93d501cb0a561a5750c97f362c"], "node": "4ea3c4873c132600584039e87ef288c502f9daad", "parents": ["920879a179a34eb5ed7dd53fe097a5a5e16149b2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1774902561, "git_changesets": ["8cefe049c93f56ae7588a89f65eb67cf118457f7"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25329": {"changesets": [{"author": "pollymce \u003cpmceldowney@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2026991: Add padding for non-edge-to-edge DohSettingsFragment.kt  a=diannaS\n\nRecently, we replaced the forced activity level window insets padding with having individual fragments opt into the padding by implementing SystemInsetsPaddedFragment. Looks like this fragment was missed out.\n\nPull request: https://github.com/mozilla-firefox/firefox/pull/162\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290798\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/main/java/org/mozilla/fenix/settings/doh/DohSettingsFragment.kt"], "git_node": "fe93ef91ef6513d0c1059fca5946519214e56bf2", "git_parents": ["8cefe049c93f56ae7588a89f65eb67cf118457f7"], "node": "89f2a078e8a6a1c826a7120fdd04056bef60ee38", "parents": ["4ea3c4873c132600584039e87ef288c502f9daad"