 height is zero) overflows. Post\nBug 1800907, the constraint was tightened so that both width and\nheight must be zero for any overflow to be ignored.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290147\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291739\n", "files": ["layout/generic/AbsoluteContainingBlock.cpp", "layout/generic/ReflowOutput.cpp", "layout/generic/ReflowOutput.h", "testing/web-platform/tests/css/css-position/position-absolute-scrollable-overflow-zero.html"], "git_node": "d66664f34c880d4c524ad2fafafe5e4523202e31", "git_parents": ["646900f2890b6973d6e10e1374db01fc9114e43a"], "node": "4264b24e3d1866768fa4f8fe3237081ca49e0c0b", "parents": ["f839e1d4cce9b7b21611a3deedac9c2974af2c3f"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775143685, "git_changesets": ["d66664f34c880d4c524ad2fafafe5e4523202e31"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25439": {"changesets": [{"author": "Byron Campen \u003cdocfaraday@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2028000: Zero this out on failure; this function is expected to overwrite it.  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291306\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291505\n", "files": ["dom/media/webrtc/transport/third_party/nICEr/src/ice/ice_parser.cpp"], "git_node": "989459bda7b5f23742b1856996e388effcc1d491", "git_parents": ["d66664f34c880d4c524ad2fafafe5e4523202e31"], "node": "754b49d7720d3eb8bab1d7cb5a9929e793da9aac", "parents": ["4264b24e3d1866768fa4f8fe3237081ca49e0c0b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775143845, "git_changesets": ["989459bda7b5f23742b1856996e388effcc1d491"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25440": {"changesets": [{"author": "Alex Franchuk \u003cafranchuk@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2027738 - Join the timeout source to the progress bar lifetime  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nThis follows the recommendation of the GLib main loop memory lifetime\ndocs.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://pha