rence to TextTrack in HonorUserPreferencesForTrackSelection.  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nAdd a kungFuDeathGrip in TextTrack::SetMode and use RefPtr in the\nHonorUserPreferencesForTrackSelection loop so that calling SetMode\ncannot invalidate the object while it is still in use.\n\nSetMode calls NotifyCueAdded for each cue, which can flush layout and\ndispatch events synchronously. A content listener can remove the track\nelement and trigger cycle collection during that dispatch, dropping the\nTextTrack's refcount to zero. The RefPtr and kungFuDeathGrip ensure\nthe object stays alive through the re-entrant call.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D289669\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290956\n", "files": ["dom/media/webvtt/TextTrack.cpp", "dom/media/webvtt/TextTrackManager.cpp"], "git_node": "a79f545223f3ec1a909e536fb1447d9e652b777f", "git_parents": ["a6c4969dacf24c1a1ffa006466b42f705ccc84ab"], "node": "8a91d3f9378cc8186937ba612cc241ebdc4151df", "parents": ["7d459d78b4841a1a27acedf2376c0211a6749dcc"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775162884, "git_changesets": ["a79f545223f3ec1a909e536fb1447d9e652b777f"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25469": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mark Striemer \u003cmstriemer@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2019762 - Match moz-badge to the design system  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nAlso create a badge/border/radius token to handle the Nova change.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D289318\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291562\n", "files": ["toolkit/content/widgets/moz-badge/moz-badge.css", "toolkit/content/widgets/moz-badge/moz-badge.mjs", "toolkit/content/widgets/moz-badge/moz-badge.stories.mjs", "toolkit/locales/en-US/toolkit/global/mozBadge.ftl", "toolkit/themes/shared/design-system/dist/semantic-categories.mjs", "toolkit/themes/shared/design-system/dist/tokens-figma-primitives.json", "toolkit/themes/shar