BUILD\n\nUpdates native menu positioning to use existing logic in nsMenuPopupFrame for handling translated elements. This fixes the position of the \"new tab\" menu on the full-screen macOS toolbar, which is translated when the menu bar is shown.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D285361\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292102\n", "files": ["layout/xul/nsMenuPopupFrame.cpp", "layout/xul/nsXULPopupManager.cpp"], "git_node": "15bd3a4cc2ece09d929646a8f275015d5b4e3de6", "git_parents": ["27c3b186adf40c6c818819b08a62bb0713ace998"], "node": "84ab4bfb7e53ecfeaa40994f1f0aba697b7db8b2", "parents": ["fa76d21f8542fec50bbf96a98a8ecd6bfa0cd1cb"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775499247, "git_changesets": ["15bd3a4cc2ece09d929646a8f275015d5b4e3de6"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25530": {"changesets": [{"author": "Karl Tomlinson \u003ckarlt+@karlt.net\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2025483 update mBeginProcessing even on speex_resampler_set_rate() error  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D290769\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292112\n", "files": ["dom/media/webaudio/AudioBufferSourceNode.cpp"], "git_node": "d9a83eabca1b81dd8160d033fca3c73c871d4b56", "git_parents": ["15bd3a4cc2ece09d929646a8f275015d5b4e3de6"], "node": "4c82832144bca6173fc4a781c39ed4d20e506b2d", "parents": ["84ab4bfb7e53ecfeaa40994f1f0aba697b7db8b2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775499879, "git_changesets": ["d9a83eabca1b81dd8160d033fca3c73c871d4b56"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25531": {"changesets": [{"author": "Rob Wu \u003crob@robwu.nl\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2028832 - Avoid inadvertent tab reversal in tabs.move to new window  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291717\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292142\n", "files": ["browser/components/extensions/parent