6 ]]\n\nThere were still 5 UI test that failed, it looks like setting privateModeAndStoriesEntryPointEnabled to false also disables the \"Stories\" settings.\n\n[[ https://treeherder.mozilla.org/jobs?repo=try&selectedTaskRun=MMC1dfZ3ShWrqC8znOOA-Q.0&revision=887c7924c69f8b834ce2ac0ac016675ef8f3a377 | Try run ]]\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291538\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292194\n", "files": ["mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/helpers/FeatureSettingsHelper.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/helpers/FeatureSettingsHelperDelegate.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/helpers/HomeActivityTestRule.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/HomeScreenTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/PocketTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/SettingsHomepageTest.kt", "mobile/android/fenix/app/src/androidTest/java/org/mozilla/fenix/ui/SponsoredShortcutsTest.kt"], "git_node": "5ebf9cbc4ca7efad6b2fe8c2ed1057277dd27659", "git_parents": ["03bdb01c1447c48e25669c63f1a9a1f7db85e4e9"], "node": "94a90e3cb380c50b51ea14448c9b9900a71da0d4", "parents": ["013dbc5301e63c584b744a92da7bbc365a427bf2"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775589496, "git_changesets": ["ab6c25b8caf811689927844b33a2657209ba56a4", "03bdb01c1447c48e25669c63f1a9a1f7db85e4e9", "5ebf9cbc4ca7efad6b2fe8c2ed1057277dd27659"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25571": {"changesets": [{"author": "Michael Hynson \u003cmhynson@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2026797 - Update VPN panel status box.  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\n- Adds a border to the status section\n- Repositions the VPN on/off button to be flush to the left\n- Updates the status icon to be 48px\n- Updates spacing around the Use VPN for site toggle container\n\nOriginal Revision: https://