99 - Swap persistent cookie storage for a dummy at shutdown.  a=diannaS\n\nThe previous fix only guarded the two PickStorage overloads against calling\nEnsureInitialized during shutdown, but there are 7 other direct callers of\nmPersistentStorage-\u003eEnsureInitialized() that were not guarded (e.g.\nGetSessionCookies, confirmed in post-fix b7 crashes).\n\nInstead of guarding each call site, replace mPersistentStorage with a\nCookieDummyStorage at AppShutdown via RunOnShutdown, and keep the real\nstorage alive in mRetiredStorage to avoid expensive in-memory teardown\nduring the critical shutdown window. CloseCookieStorages properly closes\nthe retired storage when the CookieService is destroyed.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293149\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293675\n", "files": ["netwerk/cookie/CookieService.cpp", "netwerk/cookie/CookieService.h"], "git_node": "2c22b1df663dca3d7b8f0e3bc59a0e09eb6722cf", "git_parents": ["c24d849e21dab9a39a763f5396680baabf8d6ebc"], "node": "90aa2df13563abcc266cc2fb6925c77f277399df", "parents": ["fa15d4df133648824e96dc593f789b188a2164e4"], "tags": []}], "date": 1775949898, "git_changesets": ["2c22b1df663dca3d7b8f0e3bc59a0e09eb6722cf"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25731": {"changesets": [{"author": "Release Engineering Landoscript \u003crelease+landoscript@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No Bug - Import translations from main\n", "files": ["mobile/android/android-components/components/browser/errorpages/src/main/res/values-cs/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/addons/src/main/res/values-el/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/addons/src/main/res/values-es-rCL/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/addons/src/main/res/values-eu/strings.xml", "mobile/android/android-components/components/feature/addons/src/main/res/values-fr/strings.xml", "mobile/andro