stack.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D291692\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293797\n", "files": ["dom/reporting/ReportingHeader.cpp"], "git_node": "d58d14ef16b7ee248e56cae85a48aebe3dd7aa65", "git_parents": ["219061cfbd4740db76cba1569babf202e711a1ac"], "node": "90c3cbfacb269a9d90e86b246416bead42166e8e", "parents": ["4b2ed54c30b36129972d2df7ad234df2fe28b233"], "tags": []}], "date": 1776095984, "git_changesets": ["d58d14ef16b7ee248e56cae85a48aebe3dd7aa65"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25758": {"changesets": [{"author": "Iain Ireland \u003ciireland@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2029727: Update RegExpStatics data after realloc  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292951\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293911\n", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/regexp/bug2029727.js", "js/src/vm/MatchPairs.h", "js/src/vm/RegExpStatics.h"], "git_node": "106c094bdb9e8f170013526b6be2aaa2b7e11803", "git_parents": ["d58d14ef16b7ee248e56cae85a48aebe3dd7aa65"], "node": "3ff0fa2bcaeebd67960335526e16bc1e9fa18a2d", "parents": ["90c3cbfacb269a9d90e86b246416bead42166e8e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1776096033, "git_changesets": ["106c094bdb9e8f170013526b6be2aaa2b7e11803"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25759": {"changesets": [{"author": "Julian Seward \u003cjseward@acm.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2029801.  .  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D292738\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293781\n", "files": ["js/src/jit/CodeGenerator.cpp", "js/src/jit/shared/CodeGenerator-shared.h"], "git_node": "99774cccae98d0e9e1034b20d9a8efb5e459689e", "git_parents": ["106c094bdb9e8f170013526b6be2aaa2b7e11803"], "node": "b6af3909729b817ca1094bfb67f083299395afe8", "parents": ["3ff0fa2bcaeebd67960335526e16bc1e9fa18a2d"], "tags": []}], "date": 1776096112, "git_changesets": ["99774cccae98d0e9e1034b20d9a8efb5e459689e"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25760": {"changesets": [{"author": "Greg Tatum \u003ctatum.creative@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2024354 - Implement URL tokens to reduce hallucinated URLs  a=diannaS DONTBUILD\n\nThis patch introduces URL tokens. The tokens are only applied while the\nconversation is in flight to the language model, and not when rendering\nnor serializing the conversation.\n\nCo-authored-by: Bryan Johns \u003cbjohns@mozilla.com\u003e\nCo-authored-by: Molly Shillabeer \u003cmshillabeer@mozilla.com\u003e\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D288730\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293889\n", "files": ["browser/components/aiwindow/models/Chat.sys.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/ChatUtils.sys.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/Tools.sys.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/Utils.sys.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/tests/browser/ai-window-prompts-remote-settings-snapshot.json", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/tests/xpcshell/ai-window-prompts-remote-settings-snapshot.json", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/tests/xpcshell/test_ChatUtils.js", "browser/components/aiwindow/models/tests/xpcshell/test_Utils_RemoteSettings.js", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/components/ai-chat-message/ai-chat-message.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/modules/ChatConversation.sys.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/modules/TokenStreamParser.mjs", "browser/components/aiwindow/ui/test/xpcshell/test_ChatConversation.js", "third_party/js/prosemirror/bundle_entry.mjs", "third_party/js/prosemirror/prosemirror.bundle.mjs"], "git_node": "d3efb55fc5efb991b5455b514e3ee384b3f8d92d", "git_parents": ["99774cccae98d0e9e1034b20d9a8efb5e459689e"], "node": "648d7d3d7c700401b3c2720ae87adc9492c3a9be", "parents": ["b6af3909729b817ca1094bfb67f083299395afe8"], "tags": []}], "date": 1776096516, "git_changesets": ["d3efb55fc5efb991b5455b514e3ee384b3f8d92d"], "user": "dsmith@mozilla.com"}, "25761": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jan de Mooij \u003cjdemooij@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2029735 - Handle UTF8 vs Latin1 comparisons correctly in UTF8EqualsChars., a=dsmith\n\nThe code had an assertion checking that the UTF8 string doesn't contain non-Latin1\nchars when comparing with a Latin1 string, but that assumption is invalid. This is\ncalled from the atomization code and a Latin1 string might have the same hash code as\na non-Latin1 string.\n\nIt's easy to support this by always comparing the `char16_t` values.\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293040\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293785\n", "files": ["js/src/jit-test/tests/wasm/regress/bug2029735.js", "js/src/vm/CharacterEncoding.cpp"], "git_node": "2182e1f882cfbcf86fb363366db1d4c6a78e36be", "git_parents": ["d3efb55fc5efb991b5455b514e3ee384b3f8d92d"], "node": "ed0f996ec3a165510a4645fbe3b9fafb4ae2a9f8", "parents": ["648d7d3d7c700401b3c2720ae87adc9492c3a9be"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sotaro Ikeda \u003csotaro.ikeda.g@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2029457 - Hold a reference of AsyncImagePipelineManager, a=dsmith\n\nOriginal Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293031\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D293852\n", "files": ["gfx/layers/wr/AsyncImagePipelineOp.cpp", "gfx/layers/wr/AsyncImagePipelineOp.h"], "git_node": "0507dca182947e29219d5d26e8f6d04b58370d75", "git_parents": ["2182e1f882cfbcf86fb363366db1d4c6a78e36be"], "node": "9c97cccf813c36e2767691a131cb1eed160c945d", "parents": ["ed0f996ec3a165510a4645fbe3b9fafb4ae2a9f8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Sotaro Ikeda \u003csotaro.ikeda.g@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 2027284 - Defer shmem deallocation until RenderTextureHost destruction for beta, a=dsmith\n\nDifferential Revision: https://pha